{"tid":1562600,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【區選成功爭取系列】政府正積極考慮引用《收回土地條例》","createTime":"2019-09-12T05:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T05:39:10.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11cd88e931c7ad28e0892a818d91c4af0614b8f9","tid":1562600,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:23:32.000Z","msg":"（節錄）<br />\n建聯議員劉國勳認為建議是「兩條腿走路」，指政府自己的公屋用地也未全數動工，單靠當局供應肯定追不上需求，故該黨既支持去年《施政報告》提出的「土地共享先導計劃」，利用私人業權的土地興建公營房屋；同時以作公共用途為由，引用《收回土地條例》。<br />\n<br />\n不過，民建聯強調大前提是先「逼」地產商與地主協商，「以往因為某啲原因唔能夠合併，而家逼雙方埋枱傾」，無法促成買賣才由政府出手徵地。<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，由於當局積極考慮方案，故民建聯格外進取，昨日更在報章買位刊登頭版廣告力谷宣傳，惹來泛民譏諷「早收三日風，爭取扮成功」</span>。<br />\n...<br />\n了解《收回土地條例》的人士指出，政府一向有引用該例徵地，只是收地的速度、規模及對象有所不同，估計未來將主要用於祖堂地、棕地以及業權不全的地塊，原因是發展商過去收購這幾類土地皆無功而還，當局運用公權力收地可紓緩土地短缺問題，有助加快房屋供應步伐。<br />\n<br />\n然而，上述地皮的收購程序複雜，鄉議局中人舉例解釋，根據現行條例，凡出售祖堂地，需取得所有持份男丁的同意，若有一人反對便只能作罷，以往交易經常因家庭恩怨而無法完成，「村內二房可能為啖氣，唔肯畀大房賣祖堂地，佢哋好多本身都大把錢」，令發展商收地長期「卡關」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/commentary/article/2248414/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcommentary%2Farticle%2F2248414%2F&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=3faa5f31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/commentary/article/2248414/</a>"},{"pid":"ec9e818287f8b36ebb2ad4cfe124aa887baadd57","tid":1562600,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"25bfc8c5bdcc50a75e61d24560fe0b1c94266860","tid":1562600,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:25:28.000Z","msg":"舉之將選 其言也善"},{"pid":"9a4434d5f5e2f62477abd6c642d4e2b1f09522d1","tid":1562600,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"Bin下C先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8x4f5q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8x4f5q.jpg&h=32815d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個議案提議嘅其中一個方法就係引用《收回土地條例》<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0b92663fe35087753acb6236ec29db04a21476","tid":1562600,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d50b450e4ae9e15e093c37367cb38d0382ab9c3","tid":1562600,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DStyTS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDStyTS6.jpg&h=a34a400b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/2798110200297018/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fphotos%2Fa.723529797755079%2F2798110200297018%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=f6b84a2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529